  "description": "Lakebase-backed application development kit – shared scripts, agent skills (SCM and SFTDD), MCP server, and OpenAI Foundry tool spec. Consumed by lakebase-scm-extension and coding agents (Claude Code, Claude Desktop, OpenAI Codex, Cursor, Databricks Genie Code).",
